            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, top, tail and grate your<strong> carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>mayo</strong> with the <strong>remaining chopped garlic </strong>(not a big garlic fan? Try using less!), 2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tsp] </span><strong>cold water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong> in a small bowl</p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> garlic mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
