    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>spiced</strong> <strong>beef kebabs </strong>with the <strong>pan-fried onion</strong> over the<strong> fruity couscous</strong></p><p>Drizzle the <strong>garlic mayo </strong>over the top and season generously with<strong> black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
